{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 258338, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 49562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "想象一下家里没钱穷到被迫卖淫，以及以前卖血合法化之后出现的血村", "timestamp": 1597653360, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 258342, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 49562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "以及性交易合法化之后吧，拐卖妇女儿童的犯罪率一定会大幅上升", "timestamp": 1597653416, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 258347, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 49562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "想一下荷兰红灯区的姐姐都是从哪里来的？", "timestamp": 1597653527, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 258350, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 49562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 你这两条是自相矛盾的，如果有人*穷到被迫卖淫*，当然就不需要犯法去拐卖妇女儿童了...", "timestamp": 1597653575, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 258352, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 49562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果卖淫卖血不合法 那么这些穷到只能卖淫卖血的人怎么生存呢（认真提问）\n换个角度 如果有人被迫卖淫卖血 就算这件事不合法他/她就不会被迫做别的了吗", "timestamp": 1597653588, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 258353, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 49562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "身不由己", "timestamp": 1597653592, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 258354, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 49562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 为什么旧社会让人活不下去？", "timestamp": 1597653609, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 258356, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 49562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不同意。靠逻辑建构是不能说明问题的。比如我还可以说因为没有合法的性交易，导致无法获取性行为的部分人群采取强奸等手段。", "timestamp": 1597653633, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 258359, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 49562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "还是得靠社科专业人员的研究，不能靠自己拍脑袋想", "timestamp": 1597653662, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 258360, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 49562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "之前看到过ted里一个性交易者的演讲，她从另一个角度阐述了性交易非法化对已存在性交易者的人身安全和权利的威胁，只能说任何事物都有两面性吧，合法或不合法都不是完美方案。", "timestamp": 1597653713, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 258362, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 49562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 不一样的，就像有人有原始积累的资本可以做生意，但有人就需要通过强抢来积累资本一样。就是说，当卖淫合法化之后，会出现不同类型的做生意的人，一种是招工，一种是掠夺。", "timestamp": 1597653764, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 258370, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 49562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: +1。至于拐卖的问题，通过对性服务提供人员建档是否可以避免强迫被拐卖妇女提供性服务？\n我觉得不允许合法性交易可能主要还是因为不符合所谓社会主义道德之类的", "timestamp": 1597653887, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 258372, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 49562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 哪里都会有黑市。", "timestamp": 1597653980, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 258379, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 49562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 也有道理，需要一系列数据和标准去权衡有无性交易带来的问题哪个大。有性交易之后弱者会被剥削得更多也只是我的个人感觉而已∠( ᐛ 」∠)＿", "timestamp": 1597654092, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 259025, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 49562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "看过罗翔老师的一个视频，想到一个角度是会造成对于性需求者（某种意义上的弱者）的剥削。这样看来过度zw的大多数人都是在被剥削吧，剥削正常性行为的权利？", "timestamp": 1597663725, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 260429, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 49562, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "谢谢各位，大家都好有深度", "timestamp": 1597683120, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 5, "pid": 4956